high_descs: Turn right. Walk straight. Turn Left to the round table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn right, walk straight, turn left, walk straight to the round table.
Cut the fruit into slices.
Walk to the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Take a step back to the table.
Pick up a slice on the table.
Turn right, turn right, turn right, walk straight to the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, put the apple on the top shelf. Open the cabinet, take out the apple.
Turn left, turn left to the round table.
Put the slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of apple on a table.

high_descs: turn around, then go straight until you reach the round table
pick up the knife with the yellow handle on the table
face the table again, so that you are now to the right of the black chair
slice the apple to the right of the lotion container
face the two apples on the table
place the knife, tip pointing to the table top, down between the apples
look down on the table
pick up a slice of apple on the table
turn around and face the refrigerator behind you
open the refrigerator, place the apple slice on the top right shelf, then shut the door for several seconds before opening the refrigerator and taking the apple slice out
return to the black round table and face the two apples
place the apple slice behind the other slices on the table
anns.task_desc: slice an apple and cool one of the slices in the refrigerator

high_descs: Step forward and right to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen table.
Walk around the kitchen table to face the apple.
Cut the apple on the table into three slices.
Look up to face the center of the kitchen table.
Place the knife on the kitchen table.
Look down to face the apple piece on the table.
Pick up a piece of apple on the table.
Turn right to face the fridge.
Cool the apple piece in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around to face the kitchen table.
Place the apple piece on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: To cool a piece of apple and place it on the kitchen table.
